name: THIS PIECE – ASIDES NO 010
description:
this piece

blind,
mum, sacrosanct

electric-
cipher-
juice,

like spirit,
unbound
in stratosphere,

this phantom
manifest,
this signal,
we follow

this
poetic,
chain 

this
memento
neon

transgressing
minds
and
space

breathing,
knowing

immaculate

this
matter,
like ether,
dither

sweeping
skins

we tread

we swap

believing,
accepting.
